The '''Brizzit''' were a [[Insectoid/Legends|insectoid]] [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]], difficult to identify by name and face. [[Tzizvvt]] was a Brizzit. Although he had been treasure hunting on [[Jandoon]], that was not his homeworld; though there was a colony of Brizzit established there.

[[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton's]] [[LOM-series protocol droid/Legends|LOM-series protocol droids]], which had insectoid heads designed to seem familiar to insectoid sentients, were marketed towards insectoid species such as the Brizzit.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

